articles.title: Jesse Baird: Human remains found in search for missing Sydney couple - BBC.com
articles.description: Australian police have found two bodies while searching for suspected murder victims Jesse Baird and Luke Davies.
articles.content:
By Hannah RitchieBBC News, Sydney
Police say they are "very confident" that they have found the bodies of Luke Davies (left) and Jesse Baird (right)
